init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Every year, people try to steal the mug, but are unsuccessful in their efforts.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The mug is so powerful that it will destroy the whole earth if it's put in the wrong hands.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Someone breaks into the vault and steals the mug!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They take the mug with them and use it to drink their morning coffee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The police announce that the mug has been stolen and that the thief must be stopped before it's too late.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The police officer pauses and responds.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: All of the reporters start yelling, "What!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The reporters are still in shock about the mug's special powers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The reporters looked up and saw a man flying towards them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was wet, dirty, and tired.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He had just arrived from the North Pole.
